node.text: In honor of the second edition of OVR in partnership with @artbasel, join us as we walk you through the famous Domaine du Muy in Provence.

node.title: Château d'Esclans presents an Art Walk at the Domaine du Muy in Provence

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Whispering Angel on August 12, 2021 tagging @thewhisperingangel, @fourseasonscyprus, and @moethennessy. May be an image of bottle and indoor.

node.text: It was a night to remember in Cyprus as guests dined under the stars at a Château d’Esclans rosé-paired dinner hosted by @moethennessy and @photosphotiadesgroup at the gorgeous @fourseasonscyprus. #ChateaudEsclans #WhisperingAngel #RockAngel #Garrus
